<plot>Vanda, an evil alien witch, is earth's greatest enemy. The only one to oppose her and her minions is Sport Billy, a boy who has a magic bag from which he can get whatever sports equipment he wishes. With the help of his friends Lilly and Willy and a spaceship that is also a time machine, he travels wherever and whenever he is needed to stop Vanda.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?511151</url></doc>
